      "title": "A meeting between AKD and Indian High Commissioner",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A meeting was held today (26th) between Janatha Vimukti Peramuna leader Mr. Anura Kumara Dissanayake and Indian High Commissioner to Sri Lanka Mr. Gopal Bagle.",
        "Mr. Anura Kumara Dissanayake said that the economic situation of the country and the development of relations between the two sides were discussed here.",
        "Member of Parliament Vijitha Herath, First Secretary of the Commissioner's Office Eldos Mathews have also joined this event."
      ],
